  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven or clay pot over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds, let them sizzle for a minute.",
    "Add the lamb and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add onion, garlic, and ginger, cook until onion is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add cardamom pods, peach juice, yuzu-cure, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Stir well, then add enough water to cover the lamb.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce heat to low and simmer, covered, for 1 hour and 30 minutes.",
    "Remove the lid, increase the heat to medium-high and cook until the sauce has thickened, about 20 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with fresh cilantro if desired."
  ],
